OL,6,FTom Barton talks to North East
OL,7,Fconstruction businesses one year on
OL,8,Ffrom the collapse of Tolent.
OL,10,FRepercussions from the collapse of one
OL,11,Fof the North East's biggest building
OL,12,Fconstructors are still being felt one
OL,13,Fyear on - but there are already signs
OL,14,Fof a brighter future.
