OL,3,CConstruction companies assess
OL,4,Cdifficult year after Tolent collapse
OL,6,FTolent, which was responsible for some
OL,7,Fof the most high-profile buildings in
OL,8,Fthe North East including Hadrians
OL,9,FTower in Newcastle and Riverside in
OL,10,FSunderland announced it had entered
OL,11,Fadministration on Monday 13 February
OL,12,Fdue to "significant challenges
OL,13,Fincluding the rising costs".
OL,15,FAll of the company's staff were made
OL,16,Fredundant and it has ceased operating.
