OL,6,F"I still don't think to this day that
OL,7,Fit has quite sunk in. Like what could
OL,8,Fyou do with that amount of money? It
OL,9,Fcould have been a huge investment for
OL,10,Fthe company."
OL,12,FMr Thompson's business was just one of
OL,13,Fdozens to suffer. There were seven
OL,14,Fbusinesses in the Tolent group placed
OL,15,Finto administration and between them,
OL,16,Fthey owed around #140million, much of
OL,17,Fit to small businesses.
