OL,6,FAmong those affected was a ceiling
OL,7,Fcontractor owed #360,000, a
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough joinery company owed
OL,9,F#350,000 and a Newcastle glass company
OL,10,Fowed #77,000.
OL,12,FContractors were not the only ones
OL,13,Faffected with projects already
OL,14,Funderway left searching for new
OL,15,Fcontractors to complete work.
OL,17,FAffordable housing property developer
OL,18,FGentoo spent months searching for a
OL,19,Fdifferent company to complete work at
OL,20,Fa site in Hetton le Hole in Sunderland.
