OL,3,CConstruction companies assess
OL,4,Cdifficult year after Tolent collapse
OL,6,F"It's really difficult," Joanna Gordon
OL,7,Fsaid. "It is difficult for us when we
OL,8,Fthink about those customers who could
OL,9,Fhave benefitted from those homes more
OL,10,Fquickly.
OL,12,F"But here we are we have recovered
OL,13,Ffrom that position with some small
OL,14,Fdelays on site and the end outcome is
OL,15,Fwe have some really great high-quality
OL,16,Fhomes."
OL,18,FIt was a bad year for the North East
OL,19,Fconstruction sector as a whole with
OL,20,FTolent not the only company to go
OL,21,Funder.
