OL,3,CConstruction companies assess
OL,4,Cdifficult year after Tolent collapse
OL,6,F"I don't think it is just Tolent as we
OL,7,Fhad a very bad year in the North East
OL,8,Flast year," Tim Barrett from
OL,9,FConstruction Alliance North East
OL,10,Fexplained. "We lost Tolent, we lost
OL,11,FMetnor and we lost Howard Russell -
OL,12,Fthree examples of good-sized
OL,13,Fcontractors.
OL,15,F"Turnover in the North East is North
OL,16,Fof a quarter of a billion pounds with
OL,17,Fthat alone some of the money was from
OL,18,Foutside the region, so we were
OL,19,Fbringing money into the region."
